{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_QC10_MER_610.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x1b,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0xf5,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Hmm, I wonder what's wrong... I was really, really careful when I made my decision..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Hello. Huh? The atmosphere in here is very gloomy today..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x100,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "You're probably right.<CR>I'm totally stuck."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Is it about Homunculus's jewels?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0xf7,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "Bingo. I keep selecting different jewels and delivering them, but they keep getting returned..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x76,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "What wrong with sparkles I pick!?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "Marietta, you're starting to sound like Homunculus..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x18,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "That's why I told you that you should drop the order."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x19,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "We've already sent all the jewels we could get..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x1e,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "And the last delivery included a really huge jewel that we wouldn't have made any profit from with their payment."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x196,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "But, this was the end result.<CR>Let's just give up."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x78,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "Urrrgh, I don't want to."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "Umm, can I say something?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "I've been to Homunculus Town before..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x6,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "And it's a wonderful place, but it's also a very simple place. Like, there's nothing fancy about it at all..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x1c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "I see! So that's why they're looking for extra fancy jewels!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15e,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "Umm, maybe it's the opposite... I feel like Homunculus and jewels just don't go together."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x160,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "Looking at that town, I can't imagine Homunculus wanting jewels."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x15e,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "But with this much payment,<CR>it has to be a valuable item."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x15f,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "Plus, he wants sparkles, right? I can't think of anything other than jewels."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x164,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "Hmm... But maybe that's just our sense of values talking..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "I'm sure I'll be going to their town again..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "So I'll let you know if I find anything out."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x15c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "msg_string": "Could you? Sorry to always ask for your help, Ayesha."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x193,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "msg_string": "I'll ask you as well. Please do this for us, Ayesha."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x19,
            "msg_string": "If Marietta is this determined, I want this transaction to end on good terms."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x195,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1a,
            "msg_string": "Of course. I can't guarantee anything, but I'll do my best."
        }
    ]
}